[2026-04-08T17:00:55.577Z]   From the repo root, run Freerouting:
[2026-04-08T17:00:55.577Z]     java -jar ~/.local/bin/freerouting-2.1.0.jar \
[2026-04-08T17:00:55.577Z]       -de projects/blue-dream-space/build/keyboard.dsn \
[2026-04-08T17:00:55.577Z]       -do projects/blue-dream-space/build/keyboard.ses -mp 50 -mt 24
[2026-04-08T17:00:55.577Z]   -mp  Max routing passes (default 50). Increase for complex boards,
[2026-04-08T17:00:55.577Z]         decrease to limit run time. There is no time-based timeout.
[2026-04-08T17:00:55.577Z]   -mt  Thread count for post-route optimization (your system: 24 cores).
[2026-04-08T17:00:55.577Z]         Note: the autoroute phase itself is always single-threaded.
[2026-04-08T17:00:55.577Z] 
