[2026-04-08T17:00:55.577Z]   The build generates one at projects/blue-dream-space/build/freerouting.json with
[2026-04-08T17:00:55.577Z]   headless mode, via costs, and other router settings. To use it:
[2026-04-08T17:00:55.577Z]     cd projects/blue-dream-space/build && java -jar ~/.local/bin/freerouting-2.1.0.jar \
[2026-04-08T17:00:55.577Z]       -de keyboard.dsn -do keyboard.ses -mp 50 -mt 24
